_sText: zm natalyas cottage - 64 Spawns - Radar Map - Cubemaps This is an easy-difficulty barricade camping map. It is based off of a real cottage in Ontario, and is almost 100% accurate except the furniture upstairs, the deck, and the posters on the wall. The garage and other stuff isn't quite as real but whatever. The map is pretty fun I think. Thanks go to 28 Rounds Later zombie server for testing this map.
